---
import ProseLayout from '../layouts/ProseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = new Date('2026-04-22');
const formattedUpdated = lastUpdated.toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric',
});
---

<ProseLayout
  title="Now"
  description="What Emil Østergaard is focused on right now. Updated when things change, not on a schedule."
>
  <p class="now-meta">
    Last updated <time datetime={lastUpdated.toISOString()}>{formattedUpdated}</time>. This page
    follows the <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
      >/now page convention</a
    > — a snapshot of what I'm actually spending my time on, updated when it changes.
  </p>

  <h2>Work</h2>
  <p>
    My boss of the past two and a half years co-founded <a
      href="https://umage.ai"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      target="_blank">umage.ai</a
    > with two others and brought me across as an AI Engineer. umage is an AI consultancy for Nordic enterprises
    — agentic systems, AI adoption, and running open-weight models on customer infrastructure. Right now
    I'm spending most of my time on the engineering side: building production-grade agentic code, and
    figuring out where AI genuinely earns its place in a product versus where it's just hiding complexity.
  </p>

  <h2>School</h2>
  <p>
    Fourth semester of a BSc in Computer Science at the University of Copenhagen. Currently working
    through algorithms, systems, and the kind of coursework that rewards doing the problems by hand.
  </p>

  <h2>Evenings</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Writing here occasionally, and maintaining this site</li>
    <li>
      A handful of small systems projects I keep coming back to — an HTTP server, a key-value store,
      a search engine — as a way to think carefully about tools I use every day without thinking
    </li>
    <li>Reading in Danish, English, and occasionally Russian when I have the patience for it</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Not right now</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Taking on freelance work</li>
    <li>Any new long-term commitments outside work and school</li>
    <li>Social media</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="now-footer">
    If you're reading this and we haven't spoken in a while, <a
      href="mailto:emiloestergaard03@proton.me">send me an email</a
    > — I'm slow to reach out but almost always glad when someone else does.
  </p>
</ProseLayout>

<style>
  .now-meta {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .now-footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
